Package: libkaldi
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Toolkit for speech recognition (runtime)
 Kaldi is a toolkit for speech recognition, intended for use by speech
 recognition researchers and professionals.
 .
 This package includes shared libraries required for decoding.

